1)download and install eSIM from official website of eSIM-FOSSEE. 
2)open eSIM and click on NEW PROJECT/OPEN PROJECT on upper left side of toolbar.
3)to browse the examples click on OPEN PROJECT and select any of the file under EXAMPLE folder of eSIM.
4)after clicking on NEW PROJECT give the name for project without space.
5)click on OPEN SCHEMATIC from left toolbar and create the circuit using COMPONENTS.
6)ANOTATE the circuit and then click on ERC and then click on GENERATE NETLIST.
7)exit the circuit page and comeback to main window of eSIM.
8)click on CONVERT KICAD TO NGSPICE and fill the transient response values and other relevant fields.
9)click on SIMULATION and check the outputs. 
